# Keep the Docker build context small + never ship secrets or local junk.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.expo
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.vscode
**/.idea
.git
.github
**/*.log
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.*.example
# NOTE: banco-mobile is intentionally KEPT in the build context — `pnpm install
# --frozen-lockfile` validates every workspace member's package.json against the
# lockfile, so omitting it aborts the install. Its node_modules are still
# excluded (**/node_modules above); the filtered install never pulls its deps and
# the runner image never copies its source.
# Local DB dumps / attached assets (never in an image).
database_backup.dump
database_backup.dump.gz
attached_assets
# Deployment docs don't belong inside the runtime image.
deploy/aws/reports
